&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;





Policy Reform Pathway




&lt;h1&gt;Academic-Community Partnership: From Proof of Concept to Policy Reform&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;div class="infographic-container"&gt;

    &lt;!-- Phase 1: Context --&gt;
    &lt;div class="phase-column"&gt;
        &lt;div class="header-label bg-navy"&gt;1. POLICY CONTEXT&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;Existing Initiatives:&lt;/strong&gt;
            &lt;ul&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Healthy Aging and SDOH Efforts&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Age-Friendly Health Systems&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;CMS GUIDE Model&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Medicare Diabetes Prevention&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Social Prescribing Movement&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Phase 2: Practice Model --&gt;
    &lt;div class="phase-column"&gt;
        &lt;div class="header-label bg-navy"&gt;2. PROVEN PRACTICE MODEL&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="connector"&gt;↓&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block highlight"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;Academic-Community Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;Clinical-Community Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;
            &lt;p style="margin: 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: var(--navy);"&gt;MyHealthIowa + Iowa Community HUB&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Demonstrated success in bridging clinical care and community resources.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Phase 3: Gaps --&gt;
    &lt;div class="phase-column"&gt;
        &lt;div class="header-label bg-amber"&gt;3.POLICY GAPS&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block barrier"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gap 1:&lt;/strong&gt; Financing Misalignment&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block barrier"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gap 2:&lt;/strong&gt; Fragmented Systems&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block barrier"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gap 3:&lt;/strong&gt; Workforce Limitations&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block barrier"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gap 4:&lt;/strong&gt; Infrastructure Deficits&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Phase 4: Recommendations --&gt;
    &lt;div class="phase-column"&gt;
        &lt;div class="header-label bg-teal"&gt;4. POLICY RECOMMENDATIONS&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block solution"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;R1 & R3:&lt;/strong&gt; Sustainable Reimbursement and CCH Integration
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block solution"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;R2:&lt;/strong&gt; Academic–Community Partnerships through Federal Investment
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block solution"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;R4:&lt;/strong&gt; Diversity and Community-Based Training
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="block solution"&gt;
            &lt;strong&gt;R5:&lt;/strong&gt; Equity-Focused National Quality Metrics
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #7f8c8d;"&gt;
    &lt;em&gt;Figure 1: Simplified pathway mapping the transition from identified community models to national policy reform.&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
